    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197360/extras/312ddef837a046910cfc3a7a99bec0b6.poster.avif?t=1771922909\" width=1170 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197360/extras/312ddef837a046910cfc3a7a99bec0b6.webm?t=1771922909\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197360/extras/312ddef837a046910cfc3a7a99bec0b6.mp4?t=1771922909\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >核末日降临，靠着防辐射避难所，McDoodle 一家幸免遇难，但麻烦远没有结束——补给即将耗尽，汤也快喝完了。必须有人挺身而出，前往危机四伏的废土拾荒。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不如……Mary Jane 怎么样？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197360/extras/330bdacdc0ad9bef6fbb36dbb3a0e313.poster.avif?t=1771922909\" width=1170 height=488 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197360/extras/330bdacdc0ad9bef6fbb36dbb3a0e313.webm?t=1771922909\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197360/extras/330bdacdc0ad9bef6fbb36dbb3a0e313.mp4?t=1771922909\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在随机生成的末日荒原上奔跑跳跃。你无人能挡，但敌人也不会轻易放弃。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >寻找汤和补给品，甚至还能拉上朋友加入你的无尽狂奔（免责声明：至死方休）。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >荒原之上有着数不清的致命危险：袭击者、胡乱停放的自行车、崩塌文明的遗迹、无穷无尽的突变体等等，而险中求生则是你的目标。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >造访令人叹为观止的末日后遗迹，欣赏荒凉与美丽并存的废土奇景。当然了，也别忘了收集汤，多多益善！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一次又一次地搏命狂奔，避难所的物资库等着你去填满。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197360/extras/2d169438e286e36619255d785cda2cc5.poster.avif?t=1771922909\" width=1170 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197360/extras/2d169438e286e36619255d785cda2cc5.webm?t=1771922909\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197360/extras/2d169438e286e36619255d785cda2cc5.mp4?t=1771922909\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >时间紧迫！跑啊，Mary Jane，快跑！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197360/extras/32d0508fdeef9c49c37de1496521a766.poster.avif?t=1771922909\" width=1170 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197360/extras/32d0508fdeef9c49c37de1496521a766.webm?t=1771922909\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197360/extras/32d0508fdeef9c49c37de1496521a766.mp4?t=1771922909\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
